Dockerfile with ready made Sonatype Nexus Maven Repository local mirror for nexus.OpenDaylight.org

   docker build -t vorburger/opendaylight-nexus-mirror .

   docker run -d -p 8081:8081 vorburger/opendaylight-nexus-mirror
     ==> http://localhost:8081/nexus/

   docker run --rm -it vorburger/opendaylight-nexus-mirror bash

